ton-text">See it in action</div>    <img class=3D"cta-button-arrow" src=3D"=
https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63beb0e2461232502d3d70a6/63beb0e24612322=
8593d7166_arrow-right-16.svg" alt=3D"">   </div>  </div>  <div class=3D"cta=
-image-wrapper">   <img class=3D"cta-image" src=3D"https://cdn.prod.website=
-files.com/63beb0e2461232502d3d70a6/682338b86ed507d99aa879ff_cta-EIN-match.=
png" alt=3D"">  </div> </a></div><h3>2. <a href=3D"https://www.judydiamond.=
com/products/einfinder/" target=3D"_blank">EIN Finder</a></h3><p>EIN Finder=
 from Judy Diamond Associates has over 14 million unique records that inclu=
de EINs and other information on businesses. It can find businesses based o=
n both legal and =E2=80=9Cdoing business as=E2=80=9D names, state, and/or Z=
IP code. Also, each address and EIN is verified for correctness by checking=
 it against the USPS and IRS, respectively. It also allows for doing a reve=
rse EIN search to verify whether an EIN belongs to a particular business.</=
p><p>It=E2=80=99s somewhat expensive, though, especially if you intend to u=
se it at scale. It also doesn=E2=80=99t contain much other information on c=
ompanies that could be useful for assessing risk in KYB.</p><h3>3. <a href=
=3D"https://einsearch.com/" target=3D"_blank">EIN Search</a></h3><p>Provide=
d by Liberty Data, EIN Search has over 18 million business records that inc=
lude EIN numbers verified with the IRS. It also allows for batch matching l=
ists of businesses with their EINs, as well as automated matching via API. =
Its information is only updated quarterly, though, and plans that allow for=
 API access are fairly expensive.</p><p>=E2=80=8D</p><div class=3D"w-embed"=
><h2 id=3D"verify-businesss-ein-number-with-middesk">Verify more than just =
a business=E2=80=99s EIN number with Middesk</h2></div><p>A business needs =
a valid and unique EIN to operate legally in the U.S. Verifying that a busi=
ness has an EIN and that it actually corresponds to that business is a key =
step inIt helps to determine if a business (including its owners) is repres=
enting itself accurately and is legal to do business with.</p><a fs-richtex=
t-resetix=3D"true" fs-richtext-component=3D"related-content-block" data-w-i=
d=3D"0b69fae4-47ab-89b0-a76d-a614d6c99357" href=3D"https://www.middesk.com/=
